* <tt>[[cc-mode-plus.el]]</tt> -- replaced by '''<tt>[[cc-mode+.el]]</tt>'''
* <tt>[[compile-plus.el]]</tt> -- replaced by '''<tt>[[compile+.el]]</tt>'''
* <tt>[[compile-plus-twenty.el]]</tt> -- replaced by '''<tt>[[compile+20.el]]</tt>'''
